text: Stefan Habas (born 21 April 1971) is a Polish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Poland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zakopane
